OL,3,CPolice Ombudsman to appeal High Court
OL,4,Cruling that office exceeded powers
OL,6,FThe Sean Graham massacre in 1992 saw
OL,7,Ffive people shot dead by loyalist
OL,8,Fparamilitaries.
OL,10,FIn 2022, the Police Ombudsman Marie
OL,11,FAnderson concluded the RUC had engaged
OL,12,Fin collusive behaviors with the UDA
OL,13,Fgang responsible.
OL,15,FThe term 'collusive behaviour' was at
OL,16,Fthe centre of a legal challenge by the
OL,17,FRetired Police Officers Association.
OL,19,FThe High Court ruled last week the
OL,20,FOmbudsman had exceeded her legal
OL,21,Fpowers in making that finding.
