OL,6,FErnie Waterworth from the Northern
OL,7,FIreland Retired Police Officers'
OL,8,FAssociation said: "We have said all
OL,9,Falong that what the Ombudsman was
OL,10,Fprinting and saying was actually
OL,11,Funlawful.
OL,13,F"It was wrong, totally wrong. So, I
OL,14,Fsuppose the main thing is that we have
OL,15,Fbeen vindicated.
OL,17,F"We are just so pleased about it and
OL,18,Fwe are delighted that the judge went
OL,19,Fto the length he did to explain his
OL,20,Ffindings".
