OL,6,FThe Justice Minister was called to the
OL,7,FAssembly chamber for an urgent oral
OL,8,Fquestion on the issue this on Monday.
OL,10,FDUP MLA Jonathan Buckley said: "The
OL,11,FCourt has ruled that the Police
OL,12,FOmbudsman reached conclusions outside
OL,13,Fher legal scope of office, and in
OL,14,Ffact, Marie Anderson has acted
OL,15,Fillegally and clearly from a
OL,16,Fpolitically motivated way.
OL,18,F"I believe she has compromised her
OL,19,Foffice. I believe also that she has
OL,20,Fbrought dishonour on that office in
OL,21,Fmore ways than one.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
