OL,3,CPolice Ombudsman to appeal High Court
OL,4,Cruling that office exceeded powers
OL,6,F"So can I ask the Justice Minister,
OL,7,Fdoes she agree?"
OL,9,FJustice Minister Naomi Long responded:
OL,10,F"I do not agree with the member
OL,11,Fbecause the judgment does not say that
OL,12,Fit was by political motivation.
OL,14,F"It does reflect the reality, however,
OL,15,Fthat the determinations reached
OL,16,Fexceeded the scope of the Ombudsman's
OL,17,Fpowers in the view of the courts, and
OL,18,Ftherefore that is something that we
OL,19,Fwill have to reflect on.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
