OL,6,F"The people to bear in mind, are the
OL,7,Finnocent men who were gunned down, the
OL,8,FHeights Bar in Loughinisland, Sean
OL,9,FGraham's bookmakers, and other
OL,10,Flocations.
OL,12,F"There is clear evidence of collusion
OL,13,Fin the security forces, that is not to
OL,14,Fsmear everybody who has served in the
OL,15,Fpolice and the security forces, but
OL,16,Fthere is clear evidence.
